sql_query: SELECT fm.latitude, fm.longitude, AVG(m.salinity) AS salinity_at_100dbar FROM measurements m JOIN floats_metadata fm ON m.metadata_id = fm.id WHERE m.pressure BETWEEN 90 AND 110 GROUP BY fm.latitude, fm.longitude ORDER BY fm.latitude, fm.longitude LIMIT 1000;
query: Map salinity values at 100 dbar depth
